desc_long							评测						“It is tough and unforgiving, but NeXus: One Core is also addictive and very rewarding.”8/10 – GameRamble“NeXus: One Core’s color-switching mechanic gives the game a whole ‘nother level of difficulty. It requires its players to think fast and think faster as the ship steadily gains more speed.”8.6/10 – Sirus Gaming												关于这款游戏							NeXus: One Core is fast. It is challenging. It will test your skills like only a few games did before.  Ready yourself for a extreme survival run paced by an immersive DnB Music. Set on a straight-line futurist track, your goal is to avoid obstacles while changing your ship color to pass deadly portals. Play alone or share the control of your ship with a second player in a rad co-op mode. Either way, expect not to drop your controler anytime soon.FeaturesOne of the most extreme runner out thereExclusive Fusion / Unfusion mechanics (co-op mode)Randomly generated tracksRanking system with LeaderboardsA wide range of game modesCustomizable ships						
